item.title: How to jailbreak and unlock iPhone 3GS IOS 4.2.1, old baseband
item.description: {% raw %} After wasting my evening working out a jailbreak/unlock for an old version of IOS, I discovered a side note in a devteam blog update that gave me clues on how to jailbreak and unlock my phones for the latest version of IOS.  So I spent another evening working on that. I haven't seen complete instructions anywhere yet, so here they are.  How to update your iPhone 3GS to 4.
